reviews.review_title: Very diverse, great fun to mix & match
reviews.review_buyer_description: Blue eyes, blonde hair, Porcelain skin tone, Combination skin
reviews.review_text: I use this and my Morphe Guided Desert pallet together every day to craft unique looks. From clean girl with the soft apricot and beige shades to more smouldering fox-eyes with the burnt orange and rich browns. Do yourself a favor and buy both pallets (on sale!) and you'll have a complete eyeshadow range for fair-skinned, blue-eyed complexions.
